<div><p>Se testează adăugarea unui produs prin metoda Black Box</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc28897"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P236-25: TC01-ECP-Valid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
